'''MongoDB'''是一種[[面向文档的数据库|面向文档]]的[[数据库管理系统|数据库管理系统]]，用[[C++|C++]]等语言撰寫而成，以解决应用程序开发社区中的大量现实问题。MongoDB由[[MongoDB_Inc.|MongoDB Inc.]]（当时是[[10gen|10gen]]團隊）于2007年10月开发，2009年2月首度推出，现以[[服务器端公共许可|服务器端公共许可]]（SSPL）分发。

==部署==

MongoDB社区版是免费的，可获得为[[Windows|Windows]]、[[Linux|Linux]]和[[OS_X|OS X]]二进制版本<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mongodb.com/download-center#community|title=MongoDB Download Center|work=MongoDB|access-date=August 14, 2018|language=en-us|archive-date=2018-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814232604/https://www.mongodb.com/download-center#community|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多Linux套件管理系統曾经包含MongoDB的套件，由于许可证变更，MongoDB已经从[[Debian|Debian]]、[[Fedora_(作業系統)|Fedora]]和[[Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux|Red Hat Enterprise Linux]]发行中移除。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zdnet.com/article/mongodb-open-source-server-side-public-license-rejected/|title=MongoDB "open-source" Server Side Public License rejected|last=Vaughan-Nichols|first=Steven J.|website=ZDNet|language=en|access-date=January 17, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116202120/https://www.zdnet.com/article/mongodb-open-source-server-side-public-license-rejected/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.geekwire.com/2019/mongodbs-licensing-changes-led-red-hat-drop-database-latest-version-server-os/|title=MongoDB’s licensing changes led Red Hat to drop the database from the latest version of its server OS|date=January 16, 2019|website=GeekWire|language=en-US|access-date=January 17, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117035708/https://www.geekwire.com/2019/mongodbs-licensing-changes-led-red-hat-drop-database-latest-version-server-os/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

MongoDB使用[[内存映射文件|内存映射文件]]，32位元系統上限制大小為2GB的資料，64位元支持更大的資料。<ref name="filelimit32bit">{{Cite web |url=http://blog.mongodb.org/post/137788967/32-bit-limitations |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2009-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090912155911/http://blog.mongodb.org/post/137788967/32-bit-limitations |dead-url=no }}</ref>  MongoDB的核心构件只能在[[字节序|小端序]]系統上运行，客户端库可以在小端序和大端序的系統上运行<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/administration/production-notes/#hardware-considerations |title=Hardware Considerations |accessdate=2018-09-19 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203081641/https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/administration/production-notes/#hardware-considerations |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

